tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customer_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    review_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE ProductReviews (
	review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	product_id INT,
	customer_id INT,
	review_text TEXT,
	rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE reviews (
    review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    customer_id INT,
    review_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE CustomerFeedback (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id UUID,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE ProductReview (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id UUID,
    review_text TEXT,
    rating INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
